Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时值盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟满天滚滚的积雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有穿透暑气的蝉鸣放在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林檎太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真懂行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么适合我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes  maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕  小耕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我这身怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样穿的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  怎么样  可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有大小姐的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是孕妇一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  也就是说我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去我就像是小耕的夫人一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  小农农哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为屁股太重所以掌握不了平衡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你撞我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都别闹了  电车来了  呐  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继和良田同学出发去海外研修不久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和林檎受到农的恳求一起回乡下老家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就有了暴风雨来袭的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是能顺利活下来呢  还是活不下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:44.02,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\an1\pos(100,231)}『快乐的农村』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长良川铁道  简称长铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承自旧国营铁路越美南线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在由第三Sector运营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然电车旅行就要吃什锦锅饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很入味  很入味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人的老家是什么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常地乡下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说起来这事有和你提过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农的家里有四姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上面是士姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面有工和商这对双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人最近突然回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  似乎在忙很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本来外号就叫将军嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还认为她会一直那样自由地生活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  为什么小老板会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一个人太寂寞了所以就跟我们来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然带来了也没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要负起责任照顾它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小老板  到这里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  怎么会那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在里面做了个袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小农农哟  你真的像个孕妇一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本列车正要通过第一长良川桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向我们挥手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  林檎也来挥下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我至今坐过的电车里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部电车可能是我最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢大家今天使用长良川铁道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车站工作人员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是无人车站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工和商吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐肚子也变大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商  今天这里面还有脂肪以外的东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能随便拍打哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农  耕作  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  将军大人竟然亲自来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来这肚子  哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感觉有种人妻的性感味道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这种奉承话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉幸福是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作也长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「mame」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很「mame」哟  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「mame」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打招呼时身体还好吗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  不用客气悠闲点就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marketing可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  快点回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  快坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久子伯母  喜一伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟什么要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是订婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  是谁要订婚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  当然是农和小耕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来受您照顾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谜题全部解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我们回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小老板带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被说孕妇就在那沾沾自喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了这个阴谋诡计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  小耕  大白天的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和白天有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小耕  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们学校饲养的小老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能承受住老家的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农别说是怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅和耕作的关系一点都没有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还一直对我们报告假的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家会被骗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个家伙啊  说农怀孕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从哪传出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情搞这么大是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在成立了NPO法人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要振兴村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振兴村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字为TURN  A
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是把回到乡下称为U  TURN或者I  TURN之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个的感觉类似
